- **Generator Protocol Handler**: `/packages/generator-helper/src/generatorHandler.ts`
- **Type Definitions**: `/packages/generator/src/configuration.ts` and `/packages/dmmf/src/dmmf.ts`
- **GeneratorProcess** (CLI-side runner): `/packages/generator-helper/src/GeneratorProcess.ts`
- **JSON-RPC Protocol**: `/packages/generator-helper/src/json-rpc.ts`
- **Real Implementation**: `/packages/client-generator-ts/src/generator.ts` and `/packages/client-generator-ts/src/generateClient.ts`

