## Implementation Plan: `@prisma/generator-rest-client`

### Overview

This is a standalone out-of-process Prisma generator. It uses `generatorHandler` from `@prisma/generator-helper` (JSON-RPC over stdin/stdout), reads the DMMF from `GeneratorOptions`, and writes TypeScript files to the user-configured output directory. The generator is **not** registered in `client-generator-registry` because it is an external community-style generator that gets invoked as `node ./dist/index.js`.

